{"tid":801175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天價剪髮修眉】戇男幫襯理髮店 埋單$4.6萬被嚇呆","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T14:16:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"556a58c6c30be0ced3047749916ea49ae4b52663","tid":801175,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535714852_2065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535714852_2065.jpg&h=c314bfd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪髮修眉，要近4萬元人民幣（下同，約4.6萬港元），同搶根本沒有分別！浙江杭州就有一名男子，到當地一間理髮店修髮際線和修眉，沒想到要結帳時要3.9萬元（約4.47萬港元），報警後經協調，最後也要支付2,500元（約2,866港元）。<br />\n<br />\n事發於本月28日，涉事的18歲男子小吳，到一間SPA店理髮，對方說有免費項目可以體驗，他坐下後，有人將一個單據遞給他，要他簽名。小吳表示，當時店內有兩、三個人將他圍起來，他還沒看細看，就被迫簽下單據。結果理髮及修眉後，店家卻要求小吳支付3.9萬元，隨後打折也要1.8萬元（約2.06萬港元）。小吳無奈下唯有報警，但也要給2,500元。<br />\n<br />\n小吳謂，他原本並沒有要求修眉，卻被店方強行加進去，但效果不太理想，原本他的眉毛顯示他凶惡，但修完後，同學說，他比以前更為凶惡。店方則指，收費合理，小吳雙鬢及眉毛經過處理後不會再生雜毛。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後有戲劇性發展，小吳日前在微博發文指，這次的理髮事件已經圓滿落幕，店家不僅道歉也退還所有的費用，相信是因為受到當局及網民的壓力，他要感謝一眾網友的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626946&d=9eZtiRsRI%2BHKLvqDVuibsJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=bd2871b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626946&h=82748d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626946</a>"},{"pid":"babf279ae6578d38f94273029603441fe562af33","tid":801175,"uid":27545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"如花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab376da94ec1d7d3330b002d76c85075ea62859b","tid":801175,"uid":29080,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/69/Hamgachang.gif/revision/latest?cb=20061105121804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F69%2FHamgachang.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061105121804&h=c7ab5daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"367223e21a1d10cff5d2abc1b070ffefe4a8c14b","tid":801175,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20911b365cde951d371fac626f1b323c985c978e","tid":801175,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/69/Hamgachang.gif/revision/latest?cb=20061105121804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F69%2FHamgachang.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061105121804&h=c7ab5daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83b9c14bb736a2cf1e33b4ed760525f2dcd4adc1","tid":801175,"uid":172570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20911b365cde951d371fac626f1b323c985c978e","tid":801175,"uid":100136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/69/Hamgachang.gif/revision/latest?cb=20061105121804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F69%2FHamgachang.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061105121804&h=c7ab5daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"企佢係黑人問號個表情"},{"pid":"d57a55c84daa533ec9eacbf96a8f7332ad4293eb"